									<h3><font color="#e2734e">Distributed ledgers and DeFi</font></h3>
									<p>I am working on mechanisms enabling decentralized finance and the issues of interoperbility, sovereign identity and access control over assets & information across federation of distributed ledgers.</p>
								</section>
